Wine Club: Wines of the World Wine Club Monthly Mixed Membership
List.Description: This wine club is your ticket to a world adventure in wine! Enjoy wines from well-known and up & coming wineries while you learn about the wines and varietals that are popular in certain regions. The Grand Tour wine club selects wines for their high quality and depiction of a particular region. Our wine experts personally select each wine and provide you with educational wine information and food pairing ideas.
